es%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Westminster%2C%20Nitasha%20Kaul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Kaul%2C%20let%20me%20start%20by%20asking%20you%20to%20introduce%20yourself%20to%20the%20audience.%20What%20is%20your%20connection%20to%20India%2C%20how%20long%20have%20you%20lived%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20what%20field%20of%20politics%20do%20you%20specialise%20in%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENitasha%20Kaul%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%20Karan%20for%20this%20conversation.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20born%20in%20India%2C%20as%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20online%2C%20I%20was%20born%20in%20Gorakpur.%20I%E2%80%99m%20originally%20from%20downtown%20Srinagar.%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20I%20grew%20up%20outside%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20Kashmir%20was%20very%20much%20a%20presence%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJBfPhPfzkOI%3Fsi%3DY68ZeX-hFdQzKSVM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20always%20very%20strongly%20influenced%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20civilizational%20values%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20in%20India%2C%20grown%20up%20in%20India%2C%20went%20to%20school%20in%20India%2C%20went%20to%20college%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20did%20my%20economics%20honours%20from%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20College%20of%20Commerce%20(SRCC).%20I%20was%20awarded%20a%20scholarship%20to%20do%20my%20MSc%20in%20economics%20with%20a%20specialisation%20in%20public%20policy%20in%201997%2C%20after%20which%20I%20did%20a%20joint%20PhD%20in%20economics%20and%20philosophy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20first%20career%20was%20as%20an%20economist.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half%2C%2