EBut%20this%20thing%20that%20ISI%20has%20picked%20up%20on%20it%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20live%20in%20a%20world%20of%20hybrid%20warfare%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20there%E2%80%99s%20some%20%E2%80%A6%20inimical%2C%20anti-India%20forces%20sitting%20somewhere%20clinking%20glasses%20and%20being%20very%20happy%20at%20how%20this%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20woman%2C%20who%E2%80%99s%20actually%20acting%20in%20defence%20of%20Indian%20democratic%20values%2C%20is%20being%20pillaried%20in%20this%20way%20for%20no%20cause.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20no%20control%20over%20how%20people%20selectively%20quote%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Now%2C%20Professor%20Kaul%2C%20NDTV%20has%20also%20been%20told%20that%20you%20believe%20India%20is%20an%20occupying%20power%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20treats%20Kashmiris%20like%20the%20Chinese%20treat%20the%20Uyghurs.%20Is%20that%20your%20opinion%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENK%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20No%2C%20I%20have%20not%20said%20that.%20What%20I%20have%20said%20is%20that%20we%20must%20look%20at%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20there%20are%20similarities%20and%20differences%20in%20different%20kinds%20of%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20similarity%20between%20the%20two%20regions%20is%20that%20they%20are%20Muslim-majority%20regions%20that%20are%20affected%20by%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Han%20majoritarianism%20%E2%80%A6%20Han%20chauvinism%20and%20majoritarianism%20in%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%20And%20then%20there%20are%20similarities%20in%20the%20way%20in%20which%20technologies%20of%20crowd%20control%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20deployed%20in%20these%20regions.%20And%20I%20have%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20on%20record%20as%20saying%20similarities%20and%20differences%3B%20a