anti-Semitic%20tropes%2C%20that%20Israel%20is%20somehow%20unique%20in%20being%20evil%20and%20everyone%20else%20can%20learn%20from%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20pushback%20against%20that%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20on%20record%20as%20having%20said%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20thing%20in%20relation%20to%20Bhutan%3B%20I%20mean%2C%20India%20has%20a%20long-standing%2C%20incredibly%20strong%20friendship%20and%20a%20durable%20relationship%20with%20this%20small%20state.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20example%20of%20a%20good%20relationship%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202010%20I%20gave%20a%20talk%20at%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20before%20this%20government%20came%20to%20power%20%E2%80%93%20at%20what%20was%20known%20as%20the%20IDSA%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20talk%20there%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Look%20this%20is%20such%20a%20good%20relationship%20%E2%80%A6%20what%20is%20important%20is%20not%20to%20be%20paternalistic%20but%20to%20appreciate%20the%20good%20values%20of%20that%20relationship%E2%80%99%20and%20I%20was%20actually%20really%20happy%20when%20the%20first%20visit%20of%20the%20current%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20to%20Bhutan%20%E2%80%A6%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwould-rather-stay-here-but-there-are-no-jobs-say-those-at-israel-recruitment-drive-in-haryana%5C%22%3EWould%20Rather%20Stay%20Here%20But%20There%20Are%20No%20Jobs%2C%20Say%20Those%20at%20Israel%20Recruitment%20Drive%20in%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20so%20what%20I%20have%20challenged%20is%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20should%20appreciate%20the%20legacy%20%E2%80%93%20and%20by%20the%20way%2C%20that%20legacy%20is%20from%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20first%20PM%2C%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20visit%20back