t%20the%20cafe%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Whitefield%20area%20on%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20renowned%20cafe%20was%20made%20open%20for%20the%20public%20this%20morning%20amid%20high%20security%20arrangements%20as%20customers%20stood%20in%20a%20long%20queue%20outside%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20opening%20the%20cafe%2C%20its%20co-founder%20Raghavendra%20Rao%20and%20all%20staff%20joined%20for%20the%20National%20Anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cafe%20has%20undergone%20renovations%20to%20ensure%20a%20safer%20environment%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20taking%20all%20the%20security%20measures%20to%20avoid%20such%20incidents%20in%20the%20future.%20We%20are%20strengthening%20our%20security%20team%2C%20and%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20have%20a%20panel%20of%20ex-servicemen%20to%20train%20our%20security%20guards%2C%26quot%3B%20Raghavendra%20Rao%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Karnataka%3A%20Rameshwaram%20cafe%20reopened%208%20days%20after%20the%20blast%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20blast%20took%20place%20at%20the%20cafe%20on%201st%20March%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Whitefield%20area%2C%20injuring%20several%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW9es43cIEv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FW9es43cIEv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1766272041341112397%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20Raghavendra%20Rao%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20given%20all%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20information%20to%20the%20authorities.%20We%20are%20cooperating%20with%20them.%20We%20are%20very%20thankful%20to%20the%20government%20for%20helping%20us%20reopen%20the%20cafe%20so%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNIA%20will%20soon%20bring%20the%20culprit%20before%20us.%20We%20have%20taken%20all%20precautions%20before%20reopening.%20The%20government%20and%20police%20have%20guided%20us%20on%20where%20to%20install%20more%20CCTVs.%20We%20will%20appoint%20one%20person%20just%20to%20keep%20watch%20on%20the%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20information%20about%20the%20bomber%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20blast%20at%20the%20Rameshwaram%20cafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20emphasized%20that%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20the%20informants'%20identities%20will%20be%20maintained.%20The%20agency%20also%20released%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20bomber%2C%20captured%20from%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20while%20keeping%20a%20bag%20in%20the%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%2C%20a%20popular%20eatery%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Brookfield%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20picture%20released%20by%20the%20NIA%2C%20the%20bomber%20is%20seen%20wearing%20a%20cap%2C%20black%20pants%2C%20and%20black%20shoes.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20NIA%20also%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20(bomber)%20arrest%20shall%20be%20rewarded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20declared%20the%20reward%20three%20days%20after%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20case%20to%20the%20anti-terror%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20NIA%20on%20March%203%2C%20following%20the%20visit%20of%20an%20NIA%20team%20at%20the%20blast%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20took%20place%20at%20the%20cafe%20on%20March%201%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Whitefield%20area%2C%20where%20several%20people%20were%20injured%20following%20an%20explosion%20th