es%20people%20don't%20even%20have%20complete%20knowledge%20of%20things%2C%20sometimes%20people%20get%20misguided%20on%20what%20others%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Maldives%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20not%20extend%20the%20agreement%20that%20permitted%20India%20to%20conduct%20hydrographic%20surveys%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20broke%20from%20the%20established%20tradition%20by%20opting%20not%20to%20visit%20India%20on%20his%20first%20official%20trip%2C%20instead%20choosing%20to%20visit%20Turkey%20and%20then%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709949360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F3v45k9bo_mohamed-nasheed-afp_625x300_07_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftourism-impacted-amid-row-with-india-ex-maldives-president-5204120%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohamed%20Nasheed%2C%20currently%20in%20India%2C%20also%20issued%20an%20apology%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftourism-impacted-amid-row-with-india-ex-maldives-president-5204120%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftourism-impacted-amid-row-with-india-ex-maldives-president-5204120%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftourism-impacted-amid-row-with-india-ex-maldives-president-5204120%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rain%20or%20snow%2C%20Sela%20tunnel%20will%20take%20troops%20to%20China%20frontier%20anytime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709949101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108341604%2Cimgsize-2602736.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frain-or-snow-new-tunnel-will-take-troops-to-china-frontie