20tax%20credits%2C%20down%20payment%20assistance%20for%20first-generation%20homeowners%2C%20and%20a%20plan%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20available%20homes%20on%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20proposals%20are%20directly%20aimed%20at%20helping%20people%20who%20have%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20generational%20wealth%20of%20real%20estate%2C%20helping%20them%20to%20get%20into%20homeownership%2C%20which%20provides%20more%20benefits%20than%20just%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dan%20Green%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomebuyer.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHomebuyer.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20social%20benefits%20to%20that%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20implemented%2C%20these%20proposals%20could%20make%20homeownership%20substantially%20more%20affordable%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20Americans%20who%20are%20currently%20shut%20out%20from%20owning%20a%20home%20due%20to%20the%20high%20upfront%20and%20ongoing%20costs.%20If%20you're%20thinking%20about%20buying%20a%20home%2C%20here's%20how%20Biden's%20plan%20could%20help%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Tax%20credits%20for%20homebuyers%20and%20sellers%5C%22%3ETax%20credits%20for%20homebuyers%20and%20sellers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3ETwo-year%20%245%2C000%20tax%20credit%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20called%20on%20Congress%20to%20pass%20a%20new%20tax%20credit%20that%20would%20put%20%245%2C000%20per%20year%20in%20the%20pockets%20of%20middle-class%20households%20buying%20a%20home%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Eligible%20homebuyers%20would%20get%20this%20tax%20credit%20for%20two%20years%2C%20meaning%20you%20could%20get%20a%20total%20of%20%2410%2C000%20in%20tax%20credits%20for%20buying%20a%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%20of%20this%20proposal%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20strain%20homebuyers%20are%20currently%20feeling%20due%20to%20decades-high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-mortgage-interest-rate%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EA%20%2410%2C000%20tax%20credit%20for%20sellers%20of%20starter%20homes%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20also%20kept%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fshould-i-sell-my-house-now%5C%22%3Ewould-be%20sellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20homes%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20gone%20up%2C%20many%20households%20have%20remained%20in%20the%20home%20they%20bought%20when%20mortgage%20rates%20were%20much%20lower%2C%20hesitant%20to%20trade%20their%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-mortgage-payment%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20for%20one%20that's%20much%20higher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20proposed%20tax%20credit%20aims%20to%20coax%20these%20individuals%20out%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20freeing%20up%20supply%20for%20new%20buyers.%20If%20implemented%2C%20middle-class%20families%20selling%20a%20starter%20home%20could%20get%20a%20one-year%20tax%20credit%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000.%20The%20White%20House%20defines%20a%20starter%20home%20as%20any%20home%20with%20a%20value%20below%20the%20county's%20median%20home%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%2C%20you'd%20need%20to%20sell%20your%20starter%20home%20to%20another%20owner-occupant%20(meaning%20someone%20who%20plans%20to%20live%20in%20the%20home%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20investor%20who%20will%20rent%20it%20out).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20today's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-mortgage-interest-rate%5C%22%3E%20average%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20house%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Down%20payment%20assistance%5C%22%3EDown%20payment%20assistance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20piece%20of%20Biden's%20plan%20for%20more%20affordable%20homeownership%20is%20the%20%2425%2C000%20in%20down%20payment%20assistance%20he%20wants%20Congress%20to%20provide%20to%20first-generation%20homebuyers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rationale%20behind%20this%20proposal%20is%20that%20it%20can%20often%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20break%20into%20homeownership%20if%20your%20parents%20or%20grandparents%20aren't%20homeowners%2C%20since%20your%20family%20hasn't%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20build%20that%20generational%20wealth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Lower%20closing%20costs%5C%22%3ELower%20closing%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWaived%20title%20insurance%20on%20federally%20backed%20loans%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20announced%20in%20his%20address%20that%20his%20administration%20will%20reduce%20closing%20costs%20for%20borrowers%20by%20getting%20rid%20of%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20on%20federally%20backed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%5C%22%3Emortgages%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Housing%20Finance%20Agency%20is%20launching%20a%20pilot%20program%20that%20will%20waive%20this%20cost%20on%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhen-to-refinance-mortgage%5C%22%3Erefinance%3C%2Fa%3E%20loans.%20The%20White%20House%20says%20this%20will%20save%20borrowers%20an%20average%20of%20%24750%20in%20closing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20dollars%20that%20a%20homebuyer%20puts%20towards%20title%20insurance%2C%20it's%20money%20that%20doesn't%20go%20towards%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fdown-payment-on-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20doesn't%20go%20toward%20equity%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-mortgage-closing-costs%5C%22%3EClosing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20another%20major%20barrier%20to%20homeownership.%20The%20typical%20homeowner%20will%20pay%20between%203%25%20and%206%25%20of%20their%20loan%20amount%20in%20closing%20costs%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20required%20to%20be%20paid%20in%20cash%20at%20the%20closing%20table.%20This%20can%20end%20up%20being%20a%20larger%20sum%20than%20the%20borrower's%20down%20payment%2C%20as%20many%20loans%20now%20allow%20down%20payments%20of%20just%203%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20says%20that%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20will%20also%20look%20into%20reducing%20%26quot%3Banticompetitive%20closing%20costs%26quot%3B%20charged%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Biden%20also%20wants%20to%20close%20the%20housing%20supply%20gap%5C%22%3EBiden%20also%20wants%20to%20close%20the%20housing%20supply%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2F%5C%22%3ERedfin%3C%2Fa%3E%20chief%20economist%20Daryl%20Fairweather%20says%20the%20most%20impactful%20of%20these%20proposals%20is%20Biden's%20plan%20to%20add%202%20million%20new%20or%20renovated%20homes%20to%20the%20housing%20supply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20enough%20that%20it%20would%20actually%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20the%20affordability%20crisis%20for%20housing%2C%26quot%3B%20Fairweather%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20critique%20of%20programs%20that%20provide%20direct%20assistance%20to%20homebuyers%20is%20that%20it%20ultimately%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhousing-market-predictions-2024%5C%22%3Ehousing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20conditions%20worse%2C%20by%20boosting%20demand%20without%20increasing%20supply.%20When%20a%20large%20number%20of%20homebuyers%20enter%20the%20market%20and%20there%20aren't%20enough%20homes%20to%20meet%20that%20demand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhome-prices-drop%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden's%20plan%20also%20has%20proposals%20to%20increase%20supply%2C%20including%20tax%20credits%20for%20homebuilders%20and%20rehabbers%2C%20and%20a%20%2420%20billion%20grant%20fund%20that%20the%20White%20House%20says%20could%20create%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20new%20housing%20units.%20The%20President%20also%20wants%20the%20Federal%20Home%20Loan%20Banks%20to%20put%20more%20money%20into%20the%20Affordable%20Housing%20Program%2C%20which%20supports%20access%20to%20housing%20for%20low-income%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFairweather%20says%20adding%20this%20inventory%20is%20necessary%20to%20solving%20the%20housing%20affordability%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20about%20starter%20homes%20and%20tax%20credits%2C%20I%20think%20in%2010%20years%20the%20economy%20won't%20be%20any%20different%20whether%20or%20not%20we%20do%20those%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20Fairweather%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20economy%20could%20be%20substantially%20different%20if%20we%20actually%20end%20up%20building%202%20million%20more%20homes%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20Mortgage%20is%20our%20overall%20pick%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders-first-time-buyers%5C%22%3Ebest%20mortgage%20lenders%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbank-of-america-mortgage-review%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%20Mortgage%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20hopeful%20homebuyers%20should%20know%5C%22%3EWhat%20hopeful%20homebuyers%20should%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20whole%2C%20this%20plan%20could%20substantially%20improve%20housing%20affordability%2C%20enabling%20more%20Americans%20to%20become%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20big%20caveat%3A%20The%20fate%20of%20most%20of%20these%20proposals%20depends%20on%20Biden%20winning%20the%20election%20and%20Congress%20passing%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20kind%20of%20depends%20how%20big%20of%20a%20margin%20he%20has%20in%20Congress%20and%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%20because%20I%20think%20there%20might%20be%20some%20more%20conservative%20Democrats%20who%20are%20concerned%20about%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20Fairweather%20said.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20million%20extra%20homes%20is%20going%20to%20cost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFairweather%20says%20many%20of%20these%20proposals%20likely%20wouldn't%20be%20implemented%20until%202025%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20for%20homebuyers%20who%20qualify%20for%20tax%20credits%20or%20other%20assistance%2C%20saving%20up%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20remains%20a%20big%20barrier%20to%20homeownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20there%20are%20programs%20that%20already%20exist%20today%20that%20can%20help%2C%20like%20FHA%20loans%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-first-time-homebuyer-loans%5C%22%3Efirst-time%20homebuyer%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20private%20lenders%20that%20come%20with%20beneficial%20features%20like%20down%20payment%20grants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-lower-cost-homeownership-hopeful-homebuyers-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709939058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb6fbc90413ab8e1db032a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-lower-cost-homeownership-hopeful-homebuyers-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22