0the%20Fab%20Five%2C%20giving%20people%20life%20makeovers.%20But%20the%20reality%20TV%20show's%20legacy%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2023%2F09%2F14%2Fantoni-porowski-didnt-invite-three-of-queer-eye-castmates-to-bachelor-party%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrama%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rifts%20among%20its%20cast%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reboot%2C%20which%20premiered%20on%20the%20streamer%20in%202018%2C%20was%20initially%20hosted%20by%20Bobby%20Berk%2C%20Karamo%20Brown%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftan-france-interview-baby-queer-eye-netflix-cover-story-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETan%20France%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jonathan%20Van%20Ness%2C%20and%20Antoni%20Porowski.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20interior%20designer%20Berk's%20shocking%20exit%20was%20announced%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20more%20details%20about%20the%20exit%20have%20come%20to%20light.%20Here's%20a%20complete%20timeline%20of%20the%20fallout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENovember%2013%2C%202023%3A%20Bobby%20Berk%20reveals%20he's%20exiting%20'Queer%20Eye'%20after%208%20seasons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221787%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bobby%20Berk%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BJunction%26quot%3B%20held%20at%20Harmony%20Gold%20on%20January%2024%2C%202024%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb54116080194819fe203f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBobby%20Berk%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BJunction%26quot%3B%20held%20at%20Harmony%20Gold%20on%20January%2024%2C%202024%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%3Cp%3EGilbert%20Flore%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBerk%20shared%20the%20news%20via%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbobby%2Fp%2FCznTPjYupZV%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20broken%20up%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbobbyberk%2Fstatus%2F1724110143007395881%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreads%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20full%20statement%20read%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20Queer%20Eye%20Community%20who%20have%20become%20family%20to%20me.%20The%20love%20that%20I%20have%20received%20from%20you%20all%20over%20the%20last%206%20years%20has%20been%20absolutely%20surreal.%20You%20have%20tuned%20in%20and%20been%20dedicated%20fans%20and%20together%20we%20were%20able%20to%20share%20the%20healing%20powers%20of%20design.%20I%20learned%20from%20you%20all%20about%20kindness%2C%20love%20and%20acceptance%20and%20that%20has%20changed%20my%20life%20for%20the%20better.%20The%20way%20you%20have%20embraced%20me%20and%20accepted%20me%20for%20who%20I%20am%20is%20something%20that%20l%20will%20truly%20carry%20with%20me%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%20Throughout%20these%20years%2C%20you%2C%20the%20die-hard%20fans%20of%20Queer%20Eye%2C%20have%20all%20shared%20so%20many%20stories%20with%20me%20about%20how%20the%20show%20has%20touched%20your%20lives%20and%20I%20could%20not%20be%20more%20grateful%20to%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20you%20for%20being%20brave%20enough%20to%20share%20your%20experiences.%20To%20all%20our%20wonderful%2C%20loving%2C%20amazing%2C%20and%20brave%20heroes%20there%20is%20so%20much%20I%20want%20to%20say%2C%20and%20so%20much%20gratitude%20I%20want%20to%20express%20to%20you%20all%20for%20letting%20me%20into%20your%20homes%20and%20hearts.%20It's%20all%20because%20of%20you%20that%20I've%20kept%20going%20all%20these%20years%20and%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20you%20have%20changed%20me%20for%20the%20better.%20I'm%20so%20very%20proud%20of%20all%20of%20you!%20Being%20able%20to%20help%20guide%20you%20to%20find%20the%20best%20version%20of%20yourselves%20is%20something%20I%20never%20took%20for%20granted%20and%20never%20will.%20It's%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20that%20I%20announce%20that%20season%208%20will%20be%20my%20final%20season%20on%20Queer%20Eye.%20It's%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20decision%20to%20be%20at%20peace%20with%2C%20but%20a%20necessary%20one.%20Although%20my%20journey%20with%20Queer%20Eye%20is%20over%2C%20my%20journey%20with%20you%20is%20not.%20You%20will%20be%20seeing%20more%20of%20me%20very%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20Berk's%20exit%20was%20announced%2C%20a%20source%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fbobby-berk-remains-amicable-queer-eye-castmates-source-exclusive-8401989%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20magazine%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20parting%20was%20amicable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBobby's%20departure%20is%20unrelated%20to%20relationships%20with%20his%20castmates%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20statement%20was%20contradicted%20by%20a%20source%20who%20told%20Us%20Weekly%20that%20Berk%20was%20%26quot%3Basked%20to%20leave%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20tension%20with%20the%20cast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20many%20challenges%20with%20scheduling%20%5Band%5D%20there%20was%20a%20loss%20of%20interest%20from%20Bobby%20filming%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binsider%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usmagazine.com%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2Fbobby-berk-left-queer-eye-after-challenges-with-cast-and-schedule%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUs%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20network%20and%20the%20cast%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20bring%20in%20fresh%20blood.%20His%20heart%20was%20not%20in%20it%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20started%20to%20resent%20him%20because%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3A%20Netflix%20announces%20interior%20designer%20Jeremiah%20Brent%20as%20Berk's%20replacement%20for%20season%209%3C%2