%20on%20season%20seven%20of%20%26quot%3BQueer%20Eye.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EIlana%20Panich-Linsman%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBerk's%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2Fbobby-berk-leaving-queer-eye%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20conducted%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20season%20eight%20of%20%26quot%3BQueer%20Eye.%26quot%3B%20Berk%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20he%20and%20his%20%26quot%3BQueer%20Eye%26quot%3B%20costars%20signed%20a%20seven-cycle%20contract.%20After%20the%20contract%20ended%20in%20September%202022%2C%20Berk%20said%20he%20and%20his%20costars%20were%20ready%20to%20move%20on%20%E2%80%94%20but%20then%20Netflix%20renewed%20the%20show%20and%20offered%20them%20a%20new%20contract%2C%20which%20everyone%20signed%20except%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerk%20said%20he%20left%20because%20he%20already%20had%20other%20projects%20in%20the%20works%20and%20made%20his%20peace%20with%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerk%20also%20responded%20to%20speculation%20that%20there%20was%20beef%20between%20him%20and%20France%2C%20based%20on%20his%20social%20media%20activity%20(Berk%20unfollowed%20France%20on%20Instagram%20and%20didn't%20noticeably%20tag%20him%20in%20posts%20about%20the%20group).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTan%20and%20I%20had%20a%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Berk%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20situation%2C%20and%20that's%20between%20Tan%20and%20I%2C%20and%20it%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20show.%20It%20was%20something%20personal%20that%20had%20been%20brewing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nothing%20romantic%2C%20just%20to%20clarify%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerk%20admitted%20that%20his%20emotions%20got%20the%20better%20of%20him%20and%20he%20probably%20shouldn't%20have%20unfollowed%20his%20costar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20became%20like%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20and%20siblings%20are%20always%20going%20to%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20Berk%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20hopeful%20that%20he%20and%20France%20would%20ultimately%20be%20%26quot%3Bfine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarch%205%2C%202024%3A%20Rolling%20Stone%20publishes%20a%20bombshell%20report%2C%20detailing%20behind-the-scenes%20drama%20that%20led%20to%20Berk's%20exit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(L-R)%20Antoni%20Porowski%2C%20Tan%20France%2C%20Karamo%20Brown%2C%20Bobby%20Berk%2C%20and%20Jonathan%20Van%20Ness%20in%20May%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb5297ce7f1785b2e7f1e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Antoni%20Porowski%2C%20Tan%20France%2C%20Karamo%20Brown%2C%20Bobby%20Berk%2C%20and%20Jonathan%20Van%20Ness%20in%20May%202023.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Ftv-movies%2Ftv-movie-features%2Fqueer-eye-tensions-bobby-berk-leaving-jvn-temper-1234980316%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERolling%20Stone%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoke%20to%2010%20individuals%20involved%20in%20the%20production%20of%20the%20show%20and%20%26quot%3Bwell-placed%20sources.%26quot%3B%20Among%20the%20surprising%20details%20were%20allegations%20about%20hairstylist%20Van%20Ness%2C%20who%20is%20nonbinary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20sources%20described%20them%20as%20emotionally%20%26quot%3Babusive%26quot%3B%20and%20prone%20to%20%26quot%3Brage%20issues.%26quot%3B%20Van%20Ness%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20being%20unprofessional%20and%20%26quot%3Bdemeaning%26quot%3B%20to%20others.%20According%20to%20one%20source%2C%20Van%20Ness'%20temper%20would%20hit%20a%20boiling%20point%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20absolutely%20tension%20between%20everybody%20else%2C%20especially%20from%20Jonathan%20Van%20Ness%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20production%20member%20told%20RS