rugs%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20efficacy%20has%20been%20established%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20actually%20work%20to%20treat%20certain%20issues%2C%20Barzilai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%204%20most%20underrated%20longevity%20contenders%20available%20now%2C%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35343051%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarzilai's%20research%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pills%20spilling%20out%20of%20bottle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e250cd96242f0019e7b908%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMetformin%3Cp%3EFrancis%20Dean%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetformin-diabetes-weight-loss-anti-aging-drug-long-covid-prevention-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMetformin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20one%20of%20the%20most%20widely%20prescribed%20and%20cheapest%20diabetes%20drugs%20on%20the%20market%2C%20it%20also%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20several%20key%20hallmarks%20of%20aging.%20It%20mimics%20some%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20fasting%20and%20exercise%2C%20reducing%20inflammation%20and%20cancer%20risk.%20Barzilai%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afar.org%2Ftame-trial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20large-scale%2C%20placebo-controlled%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20drug%20for%20healthy%20aging%20will%20be%20getting%20underway%20this%20year%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-rapamycin-and-how-does-it-help-prevent-aging-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERapamycin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20originally%20harvested%20from%20a%20remote%20clump%20of%20dirt%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific%2C%20rapamycin%20is%20an%20anti-fungal%20compound%20that%20helps%20govern%20a%20key%20protein%20in%20our%20body.%20It%20tamps%20down%20cellular%20growth%2C%20having%20a%20beneficial%20effect%20on%20lots%20of%20processes%20tied%20to%20aging%2C%20including%20reducing%20inflammation%20and%20improving%20immune%20function.%20Many%20biohackers%20have%20already%20started%20taking%20small%2C%20self-prescribed%20doses%20of%20it%2C%20hoping%20to%20improve%20their%20own%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EACE%20inhibitors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Angiotensin-converting%20enzyme%20(ACE)%20inhibitors%20are%20designed%20to%20lower%20a%20person's%20blood%20pressure.%20They%20keep%20blood%20flowing%20and%20can%20reduce%20stress%20on%20the%20heart.%20But%20studies%20in%20mice%20and%20rats%20suggest%20they%20can%20also%20extend%20the%20lives%20of%20animals%20with%20normal%20blood%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESGLT2%20inhibitors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Sodium-glucose%20cotransporter-2%20(SGLT2)%20inhibitors%20are%20a%20new-ish%20class%20of%20diabetes%20drugs%20that%20help%20lower%20a%20person's%20blood%20sugar%20by%20pushing%20more%20glucose%20out%20of%20their%20body%20in%20urine%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20the%20most%20expensive%20drugs%20on%20this%20list.%20In%20some%20of%20the%20most%20rigorous%20anti-aging%20research%20to%20date%20(again%2C%20in%20mice)%20SGLT2s%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20extend%20lifespan.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7710304%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearchers%20suspect%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20same%20blood%20sugar-regulating%20benefits%20of%20these%20drugs%20can%20also%20help%20stave%20off%20many%20age-related%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-promising-anti-aging-drugs-that-already-exist-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A170993374300