r%20chairman%20of%20Fox%20and%20News%20Corps%20has%20married%20four%20women%20and%20welcomed%20six%20children%20from%20the%20marriages.%20The%20media%20baron%20was%20also%20briefly%20engaged%20to%20US%20model%20and%20radio%20host%20Ann%20Lesley%20Smith%20who%20was%2025%20years%20his%20junior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20many%20wives%20of%20Rupert%20Murdoch%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E1.%20Patricia%20Booker%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murdoch%20met%20Australian%20model%20and%20flight%20attendant%20Patricia%20Booker%20in%20the%201950s%20when%20he%20was%2025.%20The%20couple%20married%20in%201956%20and%20welcomed%20their%20daughter%20Prudence%20two%20years%20later.%20The%20couple%20parted%20ways%20after%20being%20married%20for%2011%20years%20in%201967.%20Ms%20Booker%20remarried%20soon%20after%20the%20divorce%20and%20not%20much%20is%20known%20about%20her%20life.%20She%20died%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E2.%20Anna%20Maria%20Torv%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Anna%20Maria%20became%20Mr%20Murdoch's%20second%20wife%20just%20months%20after%20he%20divorced%20his%20first%20spouse%20Patricia%20Booker.%20The%20couple%20was%20married%20for%2032%20years%20till%20their%20divorce%20in%201999%2C%20marking%20the%20mogul's%20longest%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Ms%20Maria%20has%20described%20her%20ex-husband%20as%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20hard%2C%20ruthless%20and%20determined%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20that%20I%20loved%20died%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20three%20children%3A%2056-year-old%20Elisabeth%2C%2053-year-old%20Lachlan%20and%2052-year-old%20James.%20While%20Lachlan%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20as%20chairman%20of%20Fox%20Corp%20and%20News%20Corp%20last%20year%2C%20all%20three%20All%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20family%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E3.%20Wendi%20Deng%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murdoch%20and%20Wendi%20Deng%20got%20married%20just%20two%20weeks%20after%20he%20finalised%20his%20divorce%20from%20his%20second%20wife%20in%201999.%20He%20met%20the%2030-year%20old%20Chinese%20national%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20in%201997%20and%20they%20married%20in%20a%20secret%20ceremony%20on%20his%20yacht%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Deng%20is%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20movie%20producer%20and%20art%20collector%20and%20shares%20two%20daughters%20--%2023-year-old%20Grace%20and%2021-year-old%20Chloe%20--%20with%20her%20ex-husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E4.%20Jerry%20Hall%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Mr%20Murdoch%20was%20introduced%20to%20his%20fourth%20wife%20Jerry%20Hall%2C%20a%20US%20model%20and%20actor%2C%20by%20one%20of%20his%20sisters.%20After%20they%20married%2C%20Mr%20Murdoch%20said%20he%20felt%20%26quot%3Blike%20the%20luckiest%20AND%20happiest%20man%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20meeting%20him%2C%20Jerry%20Hall%20dated%20Rolling%20Stones%20frontman%20Mick%20Jagger%20and%20has%20four%20children%20with%20him.%20She%20was%20married%20to%20Ms%20Hall%20for%20six%20years%20and%20divorced%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709918400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fvv2t68kg_rupert-murdoch_625x300_08_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frupert-murdoch-to-marry-again-at-92-all-about-his-4-ex-wives-5202492%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Media%20mogul%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20is%20getting%20married%20to%20his%20girlfriend%20Elena%20Zhukova%2C%20his%20team%20announced%20on%20Friday.%20The%2092-year-old%20tycoon%20will%20marry%20the%2067-year-old%20Russian%20molecular%20biologist%20in%20July%20at%20his%20California%20wine%20estate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frupert-murdoch-to-marry-again-at-92-all-about-his-4-ex-wives-5202492%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cd