-services-to-raise-rs-2-500-crore-through-debt-capital-124030800870_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20witnessing%20asset%20quality%20pressures%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20finance%20company%20has%20improved%20its%20risk%20profile%20and%20health%20to%20support%20sustained%20growth%20in%20the%20loan%20book%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdb-financial-services-to-raise-rs-2-500-crore-through-debt-capital-124030800870_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdb-financial-services-to-raise-rs-2-500-crore-through-debt-capital-124030800870_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdb-financial-services-to-raise-rs-2-500-crore-through-debt-capital-124030800870_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20Contest%20from%20Wayanad%20Again%2C%20Congress%20Releases%20First%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01122618%2FF8oQIiNXkAA_m-k.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20on%20Friday%20(March%208)%20announced%20its%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%2039%20names%20including%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20will%20once%20again%20contest%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Wayanad%2C%20along%20with%2016%20other%20sitting%20MPs%20including%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20and%20K.C.%20Venugopal%20as%20well%20as%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Venugopal%20who%20is%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20first%20list%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%9Cwinnability%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20focusing%20on%20winnability.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20list%20that%20was%20decided%20in%20the%20central%20election%20committee%20meeting%20under%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20The%20next%20meeting%20is%20on%20March%2011%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20announced%20on%20Friday%20includes%2015%20members%20who%20are%20from%20the%20general%20category%20and%2024%20from%20SC%2FST%2FOBC%20and%20minority%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%2016%20candidates%20from%20Kerala%3B%207%20from%20Karnataka%3B%206%20from%20Chhattisgarh%3B%204%20from%20Telangana%3B%202%20from%20Meghalaya%3B%20and%201%20each%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20Tripura%20along%20with%20its%20candidate%20from%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20from%20Wayanad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20candidacy%20from%20his%20present%20constituency%20Wayanad%2C%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20INDIA%20alliance%20partner%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20announced%20senior%20party%20leader%20Annie%20Raja%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-congress-annie-raja-cpi-wayanad-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3E%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Raja%20had%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20that%20has%20to%20decide%20whether%20it%20wants%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Left%20forces%20and%20she%20hopes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20sense%20will%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20however%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20focus%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20in%20the%20maximum%20possible%20way%20to%20go%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20but%20there%20are%20issues%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Assam%20and%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20sort%20it%20out.%20Congress%20party%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20to%20reduce%20BJP%20seats%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20sacrifice%20anything.%20But%20others%20also%20need%20to%20do%20that.%20In%20some%20states%20others%20also%20need%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20still%20speculation%20about%20whether%20Gandhi%20will%20also%20contest%20from%20his%20old%20turf%20of%20Amethi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20fielded%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20repeat%20her%202019%20performance%2C%20the%20Congress%20list%20is%20silent%20on%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKerala%20surprise%20and%20other%20sitting%20MPs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20a%20total%20of%2017%20sitting%20MPs%20including%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20who%20will%20seek%20re-election%20for%20a%20fourth%20term%20from%20the%20constituency%20and%20take%20on%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20has%20also%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Rajnandgaon%20constituency.%20He%20will%20take%20on%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20sitting%20MP%20Santosh%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20however%20dropped%20a%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thrissur%20constituency%20T.N.%20Prathapan%20and%20instead%20fielded%20K.%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20field%20Muraleedharan%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Vadakara%2C%20from%20Thrissur%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20his%20sister%20Padmaja%20Venugopal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-congress-there-is-no-leadership-padmaja-venugopal-joins-bjp-5195697%5C%22%3Ejoining%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20saffron%20party%20in%20its%20list%20announced%20last%20week%2C%20has%20however%20fielded%20Suresh%20Gopi%20from%20Thrissur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20who%20is%20a%20sitting%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20will%20also%20contest%20the%20elections%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Alappuzha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20MPs%20that%20have%20been%20fielded%20include%20Jyotsna%20Mahant%20from%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Korba%2C%C2%A0%20Kerala%20MPs%20V.K%20Sreekandan%20(Palakkad)%2C%20M.K%20Raghavan%20(Kozhikode)%2C%20K.%20Sudhakaran%20(Kannur)%2C%20Rajmohan%20Unnithan%20(Kasargod)%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%20(Alathur)%2C%20Beny%20Behanan%20(Chalakundy)%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%20(Ernakulam)%2C%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20(Idukki)%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(Thiruvananthapuram)%2C%20K%20Suresh%20(Mavelikkara)%2C%20Anto%20Antony%20(Pathanamthitta)%2C%20Adoor%20Prakash%20(Attingal)%2C%20and%20Vincent%20H%20Pala%20from%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20Shillong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20headway%20with%20TMC%2C%20Meghalaya%20candidates%20named%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20indication%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20not%20making%20headway%2C%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fimportant-pillar-of-the-india-bloc-congress-after-tmc-reiterates-solo-act-for-bengal%5C%22%3Eassurances%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Congress%20top%20leadership%20that%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20candidates%20for%20the%20two%20seats%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPala%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Shillong%20has%20been%20named%20once%20again%20along%20with%20Saleng%20A%20Sangma%20from%20Tura.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheshillongtimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F29%2Fcongress-tmc-eye-tura-seat-together%2F%5C%22%3ETalks%20were%20being%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20TMC%20over%20the%20Tura%20seat%20to%20take%20on%20Agatha%20Sangma%20of%20the%20National%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party-an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20however%20Banerjee%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20TMC%20would%20go%20it%20solo%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20states%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Baghel%2C%20and%20sitting%20MP%20Mahant%20the%20party%20has%20also%20named%20Tamradwajh%20Sahu%20sitting%20MLA%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20from%C2%A0%20Mahasamund.%20In%20addition%2C%20former%20state%20minister%20Shivkumar%20Dahariya%20has%20been%20named%20from%20Jangir%20Champa%20along%20with%20Rajendra%20Sahu%20from%20Durg%20where%20he%20will%20take%20on%20sitting%20BJP%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel.%20Former%20MLA%20Vikas%20Upadhyay%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20state%20capital%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%20senior%20party%20leader%20K%20Jana%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Raghuveer%20Kunduru%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Nalgonda%2C%20along%20with%20AICC%20secretary%20C%20Vamshi%20Chand%20Reddy%20from%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20Balram%20Naik%20Poikra%20from%20Mahbubabad%20and%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Shetkar%20from%20Zahirabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tripura%2C%20the%20party%20has%20fielded%20its%20state%20president%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Saha%20from%20Tripura%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland%20Congress%20chief%20SS%20Jamir%20and%20Sikkim%20Congress%20chief%20Gopal%20Chettri%20have%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20lone%20seats%20in%20the%20respective%20states.%20Former%20MP%20Mohd%20Hamdullah%20Sayeed%20has%20been%20named%20as%20the%20candidate%20for%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709915747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01122618%2FF8oQIiNXkAA_m-k.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-polls-rahul-gandhi-to-contest-from-wayanad-again-congress-releases-first-list%22%2C