lections-could-shape-the-world-13089976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20over%2050%20countries%20going%20to%20the%20polls%2C%202024%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20record%20year%20for%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20making%20this%20a%20key%20year%20for%20global%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhow-2024s-global-elections-could-shape-the-world-13089976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-2024s-global-elections-could-shape-the-world-13089976%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-2024s-global-elections-could-shape-the-world-13089976%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20the%20CAA%20Rules%20Unravel%20a%20'Chronology'%20That%20Lets%20Loose%20an%20NRC-NPR%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18134115%2FTricolour-used-in-Shaheen-Bagh-against-the-CAA-NRC-as-a-alrge-section-of-muslims-had-to-prove-their-citizenship.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECitizens%20activism%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20has%20revealed%20how%20a%20giant%20step%20towards%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20and%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20has%20been%20possibly%20taken%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20when%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20NPR%20database%20in%202015.%20The%20creation%20of%20an%20NPR%20database%20began%20first%20in%202010%20and%20was%20abandoned%20thereafter%20due%20to%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20only%20legal%20way%20of%20linking%20the%20two%20databases%20is%20by%20acquiring%20informed%20consent%20from%20every%20resident%20through%20an%20exercise%20similar%20to%20the%20Census%2C%20which%20means%20through%20a%20public%20exercise%20conducted%20by%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%2C%20the%20process%20appears%20to%20have%20happened%20without%20any%20informed%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20yet%20another%20angle%20or%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20nationwide%20agitation%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20NPR%20and%20NRC%2C%20the%20union%20government%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20Census%20(now%20not%20conducted%20since%202011%20and%20which%20was%20statutorily%20due%20in%202021)%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20with%20the%20NPR%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20outcry%20of%20protest%20against%20this%20move%20as%20several%20state%20governments%20called%20for%20a%20boycott%20against%20answering%20questions%20pertaining%20to%20NPR%20in%20the%20Census%20form.%20Four%20specific%20questions%20were%20included%20in%20the%20Census%20form%20related%20to%20the%20NPR-NRC.%20For%20instance%2C%20information%20related%20to%20parents%E2%80%99%20places%20and%20dates%20of%20birth%20were%20sought.These%20are%20not%20answers%20that%20Census%20data%20ever%20seeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushed%20into%20a%20corner%20by%20several%20unaffiliated%20state%20governments%2C%20the%20home%20ministry%20was%20compelled%20to%20admit%20that%20answering%20questions%20in%20the%20NPR%20is%20purely%20voluntary%20while%20under%20the%20Census%20Act%2C%201948%2C%20there%20is%20a%20legal%20obligation%20to%20answer%20all%20the%20questions%20put%20every%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Census%20process%20is%20oral%20and%20conducted%20by%20designated%20officers%20of%20the%20RGI%20without%20any%20document%20that%20takes%20or%20asks%20for%20signatures.%20The%20census%20data%20collection%2C%20house-listing%20and%20household%20data%20collection%20is%20crucial%20for%20understanding%20demographics%20and%20formulation%20of%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20enumeration%20for%20the%20NPR%20can%20only%20be%20conducted%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Registration%20of%20Citizens%20and%20Issue%20of%20National%20Identity%20Cards)%20Rules%2C%202003%20which%20in%20fact%20goes%20beyond%20the%20amended%20Section%2014A%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955%20(amended%20in%202004)%20and%20is%20therefore%20arguably%20ultra%20vires%20of%20the%20act%20itself%3B%20Section%2014A%20of%20the%20amended%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955%20(amendment%20in%202004)%20simply%20states%20that%20the%20government%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20compulsorily%20register%20every%20citizen%20as%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20and%20issue%20a%20national%20identity%20card%20to%20him%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20the%20rules%20that%20ascribe%20the%20process%20of%20NPR%20enumeration%20not%20the%20act.%20Both%20Section%2014A%20and%20the%20rules%20are%20currently%20under%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20background%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20share%20information%20publicly%2C%20also%20given%20its%20doubtful%20credentials%20over%20data%20collection%20and%20maintenance%20of%20data%20integrity%2C%202023%20brought%20another%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%5C%22%3ERules%20Under%20CAA%20Now%20Ready%2C%20Likely%20to%20Be%20Notified%20Before%202024%20Elections%3A%20Reports%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Annual%20Report%202021-22%20of%20MHA%20declared%20that%20crucial%20personal%20data%20%E2%80%93%20that%20can%20only%20be%20collected%20through%20a%20rigorous%20door-to-door%20enumeration%20process%20by%20officials%20under%20the%20RGI%20and%20which%20includes%20name%2C%20gender%2C%20date%20and%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20place%20of%20residence%2C%20father%E2%80%99s%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20(already)%20collected%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20secretive%20manner%2C%20by%20seeding%20Aadhaar%2C%20mobile%20numbers%20and%20ration%20card%20details.%20A%20series%20of%20RTIs%20has%20led%20us%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20exercise%20was%20conducted%20%3Cem%3Ew%3C%2Fem%3Eithout%20the%20informed%20consent%20of%20Indians.%20A%20further%20scrutiny%20of%20home%20ministry%20reports%20of%202010%2C%202015-2016%20and%202020%20raises%20more%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20scale%20of%20NPR-Aadhaar%20linkage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20of%20the%20NPR%20updated%20records%20contain%20details%20from%20the%20Aadhaar%20card%20and%20have%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%202020%20NPR%20manual%20mentions%20that%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20in%20the%20NPR%20booklet%20came%20from%20the%202015-2016%20exercise%20of%20%E2%80%9Cupdating%20the%20NPR%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20RGI%20is%20silent%20on%20this%20and%20repeated%20efforts%20to%20seek%20replies%20from%20the%20RGI%20under%20the%20RTI%C2%A0have%20not%20helped%20clarify%20the%20exact%20scale%20of%20the%20linkage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cu%3E%202014-15%20a%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cu%3Ennual%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%20of%20the%20home%20ministry%20mentioned%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdata%20digitisation%20process%20has%20been%20completed%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20database%20of%20%E2%80%9C119.19%20crore%20persons%20created.%E2%80%9D%20The%3Cu%3E%202017-18%20annual%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%20of%20the%20ministry%20contradicts%20this%20and%20underlines%20%E2%80%9Cdemographic%20data%20of%20119.95%20crore%20persons%20was%20collected%20in%202010%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20during%202015-%2016%20in%20all%20States%2FUTs%20except%20Assam%20and%20Meghalaya%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20several%20annual%20reports%20of%20MHA%20that%20give%20a%20count%20of%20the%20NPR%20records%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20those%20reports%20correspond%20to%20the%20period%20before%20the%20updating%20exercise%20of%202015-16.%20The%20a%3Cu%3Ennual%20report%20of%202014-15%3C%2Fu%3E%20states%20that%20the%20NPR%20data%20of%20more%20than%2023.51%20crore%20persons%20has%20been%20%3Cstrong%3Eset%20to%20UIDAI%20for%20duplication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20generation%20of%20Aaadhaar%20number%2C%20of%20which%20UIDAI%20generated%2019.67%20crore%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20which%20is%20in%20turn%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%2080.46%20crore%20Aadhaar%20database%20generated%20by%20UIDAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20are%20several%20annual%20reports%20of%20MHA%20that%20give%20a%20count%20of%20the%20NPR%20records%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20those%20reports%20correspond%20to%20the%20period%20before%20the%20updating%20exercise%20of%202015-16.%20The%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ennual%20report%20of%202014-15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20states%20that%20the%20NPR%20data%20of%20more%20than%2023.51%20crore%20persons%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebeen%20sent%20to%20UIDAI%20for%20duplication%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%C2%A0this%20means%20seeding%20of%20data%20collected%20for%20purposes%20for%20proof%20of%20residence%2C%20Aadhaar%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20generation%20of%20Aaadhaar%20number%20being%20used%20as%20base%20data%20for%20the%20NPR.%20From%20this%2023.51%20crore%20strong%20data%20of%20Aadhaar%20records%20UIDAI%20generated%2019.67%20crore%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20which%20is%20in%20turn%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%2080.46%20crore%20Aadhaar%20database%20generated%20by%20UIDAI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20number%20could%20only%20have%20grown%20after%20the%202015-16%20exercise%2C%20which%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20a%20giant%20leap%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20linkage.%20The%20official%20records%20are%20clear%20that%20the%20leap%20did%20take%20place%20but%20unclear%20on%20the%20scale%20or%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20the%20NPR-Aadhaar%20linkage%20illegal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NPR%20database%20is%20distinct%20from%20the%20Aadhaar%20database.%20The%20former%20draws%20strength%20from%20the%20amended%20section%2014A%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%20that%20provides%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20National%20Identity%20Card%20for%20Citizens%20(rules%20outline%20the%20NPR%20as%20the%20procedure%20to%20achieve%20this).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aadhaar%20card%20is%20simply%20a%20proof%20of%20residence%2C%20with%20biometric%20data%20collection%20to%20enable%20access%20to%20government%20schemes%20etc.%20The%20legal%20provision%20for%20Aadhaar%20came%20through%20the%3Cu%3E%20Aadhaar%20Act%20of%202016%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20which%20made%20informed%20consent%20of%20the%20holder%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20mandatory%20for%20its%20use%20for%20any%20specific%20purpose.%20After%20the%202018%20judgement%20in%20the%20Aadhaar%20case%20limiting%20its%20proliferation%20(that%20struck%20down%20Section%2057%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20Act%20that%20enabled%20private%20entities%20to%20use%20Aadhaar%20data%20for%20services)%2C%20serious%20issues%20of%20policy%20incursions%20into%20privacy%20have%20also%20been%20flagged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20complex.%20In%202010%2C%20an%20exercise%20thereafter%20amended%2C%20demographic%20information%20for%20the%20NPR%20were%20collected%20through%20a%20door-to-door%20enumeration%20process%20conducted%20by%20RGI%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20signed%20form%3B%20thereafter%20this%20exercise%20was%20abandoned.%20The%20Aadhaar%20number%20was%20assigned%20by%20the%20UIDAI%20authorities%20after%20the%20collection%20of%20biometric%20data%20including%20photographs%2C%20ten%20fingerprints%20and%20IRIS%20prints.%20The%20Aadhaar%20number%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20link%20between%20the%20records%20of%20one%20person%20in%20the%20two%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%3Cu%3E%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202003%3C%2Fu%3E%20did%20not%20provide%20for%20the%20linking%20of%20databases%20controlled%20by%20two%20different%20agencies.%20The%20data%20for%20Aadhaar%20had%20actually%20been%20collected%20by%20various%20private%20agencies%20through%20camps%2C%20and%20not%20through%20any%20door-to-door%20visit%20by%20enumerators%20engaged%20by%20RGI.%20The%20wholesale%20linkage%20that%20happened%20till%202015%2C%20without%20specific%20consent%20of%20any%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20holders%2C%20was%20not%20backed%20by%20that%20law%20or%20any%20other%20law.%20Thus%2C%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20NPR%20%E2%80%93%20as%20of%202015%20%E2%80%93%20is%20highly%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20NPR%20has%20been%20to%20establish%20residency%20(and%20then%20citizenship)%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20documentation%2C%20shifting%20the%20burden%20of%20proof%20on%20an%20individual%20that%20will%20then%20expose%20himself%20to%20the%20tyranny%20of%20a%20local%20bureaucracy%20controlled%20by%20governments.%20Absence%20or%20anomalies%20in%20these%20documents%20will%20lead%20to%20arbitrary%20exclusions%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cordinary%20residents%E2%80%9D%20(citizenship%20list)%20causing%20untold%20hardships%20and%20social%20upheavals.%20As%20the%20lived%20current%20experience%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Assam%20reveals.%20The%20exercise%20is%20not%20just%20fundamentally%20unfair%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eultra%20vires%3C%2Fem%3E%20process%20exposes%20the%20defenceless%20individual%20to%20the%20judgment%20of%20local%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202019%2C%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20religion%20biased%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(2019)%20caused%20outrage.%20Assertions%20by%20senior%20functionaries%20of%20the%20present%20union%20government%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA-NPR-NRC%20would%20%E2%80%9Cfollow%20a%20chronology%E2%80%9D%20led%20to%20legitimate%20fears%20that%20this%20was%20the%20aggressive%20first%20step%20to%20use%20the%20tyranny%20of%20a%20bureaucratic%20document%20test%20to%20exclude%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20disempowered%20and%20marginalised%20Indians%20from%20their%20citizenship.%20Now%20fears%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cchronology%E2%80%9D%20being%20set%20in%20motion%20any%20day%20may%20be%20realised%20as%20the%20CAA%20Rules%20(pending%20since%202019%20when%20the%20Act%20was%20passed)%20are%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20spent%20Rs%201%2C700%20crore%20from%20the%20public%20exchequer%20on%20an%20excruciating%20exercise%20that%20has%20burdened%20not%20just%20the%20state%20but%20a%20third%20plus%20of%20the%203.3%20crore%20population%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20least%201.3%20crore%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20are%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%20affected%20by%20the%20citizenship%20crisis.%20Arbitrary%20exclusions%20have%20been%20marked%20by%20baseless%20%E2%80%9Cnotices%E2%80%9D%20being%20sent%20by%20the%20Assam%20Border%20Police%20and%20Foreigner%20Tribunals%20(adjudicating%20bodies%20controlled%20by%20the%20state%20executive)%20and%20while%20a%20significant%202%2C22%2C000%20citizens%20and%20their%20families%20reel%20under%20the%20burden%20of%20either%20being%20excluded%20from%20the%20NRC%20or%20being%20declared%20%E2%80%9Csuspected%20foreigners%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CD%E2%80%9D%20Voters%2C%20our%20experience%20on%20the%20ground%20shows%20that%2099%25%20or%20more%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgenuine%E2%80%99%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-why-the-bjp-brings-up-the-caa-but-stops-short-of-implementing-it-in-bengal%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20Why%20the%20BJP%20Brings%20up%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Stops%20Short%20of%20Implementing%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20linkage%20of%20NPR%20with%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%2C%20without%20informed%20consent%20and%20in%20a%20hasty%20and%20secretive%20manner%2C%20creates%20further%20possibility%20of%20anomalies%20and%20mismatch%20in%20documents%20Added%20to%20this%2C%20the%20the%20proviso%2C%20contained%20in%20the%202003%20Rules%20that%20shift%20the%20burden%20of%20proof%20on%20individuals%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprove%E2%80%9D%20citizenship%20is%20a%20recipe%20made%20for%20large-scale%20social%20disaster%20and%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20belated%20realisation%20that%20had%20most%20likely%20led%20the%20MHA%20to%20abandon%20the%20pilot%20project%20begun%20earlier%20(obliquely%20referred%20to%20MHA%3Cu%3E%20annual%20report%202008-09).%20%3C%2Fu%3EThe%20complication%20referred%20to%20here%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20documentation%20of%20genuine%20citizens%20in%20this%20country%2C%20and%20also%20the%20imbalance%20of%20the%20power%20equation%20between%20the%20common%20man%20and%20the%20local%20face%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20same%20complications%20apply%20equally%20to%20genuine%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20union%20government%20that%20is%20truly%20representative%20of%20all%20Indians%20will%2C%20from%20the%20Assam%20experience%2C%20understand%20this%20problem.%20An%20unaccountable%20regime%20may%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20collective%20citizens%E2%80%99%20investigation%20by%20Metiabruz%20Kolkatta%20in%20close%20collaborators%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcjp.org.in%5C%22%3ECitizens%20for%20Justice%20and%20Peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETeesta%20Seetalvad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20secretary%20of%20Citizens%20for%20Justice%20and%20Peace.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709908053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18134115%2FTricolour-used-in-Shaheen-Bagh-against-the-CAA-NRC-as-a-alrge-section-of-muslims-had-to-prove-their-citizenship.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwill-the-caa-rules-unravel-a-chronology-that-lets-loose-an-nrc-npr%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Union%20government%20that%20is%20truly%20representative%20of%20all%20Indians%20will%2C%20from%20the%20Assam%20experience%2C%20understand%20this%20problem.%20An%20unaccountable%20regime%20may%20not.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwill-the-caa-rules-unravel-a-chronology-that-lets-loose-an-nrc-npr%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cong%20releases%20first%20list%20of%2039%20candidates%2C%20Rahul%20to%20contest%20from%20Wayanad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709908029000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F07%2Ffull%2F1709815920-3923.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcong-releases-first-list-of-39-candidates-rahul-to-contest-from-wayanad-124030800783_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Venugopal%20said%20the%20list%20has%2015%20general%20category%20candidates%20while%2024%20are%20from%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%20and%20minority%20communities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcong-releases-first-list-of-39-candidates-rahul-to-contest-from-wayanad-124030800783_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcong-releases-first-list-of-39-candidates-rahul-to-contest-from-wayanad-124030800783_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcong-releases-first-list-of-39-candidates-rahul-to-contest-from-wayanad-124030800783_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20teenager%20replaces%20Carlos%20Sainz%20for%20Ferrari%20in%20qualifying%20ahead%20of%20Saudi%20Arabian%20Grand%20Prix%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709908020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-oliver-bearman-ferrari_6483445.jpg%3F20240308183932%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-