day%20(March%207)%2C%20spanning%2015%20locations%20across%20seven%20cities%2C%20were%20prompted%20by%20complaints%20of%20human%20trafficking%20against%20visa%20consultancy%20firms%20and%20agents%20for%20sending%20Indians%20to%20Russia%20purportedly%20for%20employment%2C%20only%20to%20compel%20them%20into%20frontline%20deployment%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20many%20were%20lured%20to%20Russia%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20securing%20admission%20into%20private%20universities%20and%20then%20forced%20to%20go%20to%20the%20war%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20Friday%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20several%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20duped%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Indian%20army.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20strongly%20taken%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Russian%20government%20for%20the%20early%20discharge%20of%20such%20Indian%20nationals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20remain%20committed%20to%20the%20early%20release%20of%20our%20nationals%20serving%20as%20support%20staff%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army%20and%20their%20eventual%20return%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20raids%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20CBI%20had%20%E2%80%9Cbusted%20a%20major%20human%20trafficking%20network%20conducting%20searches%20in%20several%20cities%20and%20collecting%20incriminating%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20action%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20initiated%20against%20%E2%80%9Cagents%20and%20unscrupulous%20elements%20who%20recruited%20them%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20of%20human%20trafficking%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20several%20agents%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20spokesperson%20also%20reiterated%20that%20Indian%20nationals%20should%20not%20be%20swayed%20by%20offers%20for%20support%20jobs%20with%20the%20Russian%20army%20as%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfraught%20with%20danger%20and%20risk%20to%20life%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhyderabad-man-allegedly-forced-to-join-russian-army-dies-in-ukraine-war%5C%22%3Etwo%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2F23-year-old-indian-national-hired-as-security-helper-in-russia-killed-in-war-zone%5C%22%3EIndians%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20were%20working%20with%20the%20Russian%20army%2C%20are%20known%20to%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20fighting.%20The%20MEA%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20since%20they%20were%20killed%20in%20distant%20locations%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20had%20been%20facing%20challenges%20to%20get%20their%20mortal%20remains%20back%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcbi.gov.in%2Fpress-detail%2FNjE2MQ%3D%3D%5C%22%3EThe%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctraffickers%20have%20been%20operating%20as%20an%20organised%20network%20and%20were%20luring%20Indian%20nationals%20through%20social%20media%20channels%20like%20YouTube%20etc.%20and%20also%20through%20their%20local%20contacts%2Fagents%20for%20highly%20paid%20jobs%20in%20Russia%E2%80%9D.%20The%20raids%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Ambala%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Madurai%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%20and%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reaching%20Russia%2C%20the%20Indians%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20trained%20in%20combat%20roles%20and%20deployed%20at%20the%20front%20bases%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20zone%20against%20their%20wishes%2C%20thus%2C%20putting%20their%20lives%20in%20grave%20danger%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20raid%2C%20the%20CBI%20found%20cash%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20confiscated%20%E2%80%9Cincriminating%20documents%20and%20electronic%20records%20like%20laptops%2C%20mobiles%2C%20desktops%2C%20CCTV%