business-granting-interviews-on-pending-matter-supreme-court-seeks-clarification-from-calcutta-hc-justice-abhijit-gangopadhyay-227057%5C%22%3Egranting%20an%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20criticised%20a%20political%20leader.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20top%20court%20requested%20that%20a%20case%20involving%20the%20politician%20be%20moved%20from%20Justice%20Ganguly%E2%80%99s%20court%20to%20maintain%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202023%2C%20Justice%20Ganguly%20ordered%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20lawyer%20in%20his%20courtroom%2C%20prompting%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-justice-abhijit-gangopadhyay-bars-boycott-call-after-calcutta-high-court-judge-orders-lawyers-arrest-4701254%5C%22%3Eboycott%3C%2Fa%3E%20him.%20This%20incident%20further%20fuelled%20public%20debate%20about%20his%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20after%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20overturned%20his%20ruling%2C%20Justice%20Ganguly%20made%20public%20accusations%20against%20one%20of%20the%20judges%2C%20questioning%20his%20impartiality%20and%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20order.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20intervened%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20actions%2C%20Justice%20Ganguly%20also%20made%20public%20statements%20that%20were%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20controversial.%20These%20included%20questioning%20a%20prominent%20family%E2%80%99s%20property%20holdings%20and%20proposing%20unconventional%20solutions%20to%20social%20issues%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20his%20judicial%20temperament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709904907000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08170331%2Fimage-1922.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http